name: A Useless Gesture
Lore: 'Imperial officers aboard the Death Star considered the Rebellion a minor threat.',
Text: 'Plays on table. Cancels Don''t Underestimate Our Chances. When opponent plays an Interrupt and has 3 smugglers on table, if that Interrupt is placed in Lost Pile, place it out of play. Ketwol may exchange a docking bay only once per game.',
